# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Coolify Environment Configuration
# Copy these to Coolify's Environment section
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# REQUIRED - YOU MUST SET THESE
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

MONGO_PASSWORD=CHANGE_THIS_TO_SECURE_PASSWORD

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OPTIONAL - Only if using external AI services
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# HF_TOKEN=your_huggingface_token_here

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# EVERYTHING BELOW HAS SMART DEFAULTS
# No changes needed unless customizing
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Database
MONGO_USERNAME=admin
DB_NAME=webscraper

# Data Storage (uses your /data directory)
DATA_PATH=/data

# Service Ports
GATEWAY_PORT=8000
N8N_PORT=5678
OLLAMA_PORT=11434
MONGO_PORT=27017

# AI Models (defaults optimized for quality)
VISION_MODEL=llava
OCR_MODEL=llava
EXTRACTION_MODEL=llama3.1
EMBEDDING_MODEL=bge-m3

# Performance (optimized for 32GB RAM server)
MAX_CONCURRENT_REQUESTS=20
OLLAMA_NUM_PARALLEL=4
OLLAMA_MAX_LOADED_MODELS=3

# n8n (Coolify auto-configures)
N8N_HOST=${COOLIFY_FQDN}
N8N_PROTOCOL=https
WEBHOOK_URL=https://${COOLIFY_FQDN}
TIMEZONE=America/New_York

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# INTERNAL - Automatically configured by Docker
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════

MONGODB_URI=mongodb://${MONGO_USERNAME}:${MONGO_PASSWORD}@mongodb:27017
OLLAMA_URL=http://ollama:11434
DISCOVERY_URL=http://agent-discovery:8001
CAMOUFOX_URL=http://agent-camoufox:8002
VISION_URL=http://agent-vision:8003
EXTRACTION_URL=http://agent-extraction:8004
